on]]\n| 2018<ref name=\"Josh Sims\"/>\n| 2019<ref name=\"Josh Sims\"/>\n| 16\n| 0\n|-\n| 20\n| [[Tiago Ilori]]{{refn|group=lower-alpha|name=IloriNat|Tiago Ilori was born in [[Hampstead]], [[England]], but qualified to represent [[Portugal]] through his mother, representing Portugal at U18, U19, U20, U21 and U23 level.}}\n| {{flagicon|POR}}\n| DF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2019|5|5|1993|2|26}}\n| [[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]]\n| 2017<ref name=\"Ilori LFC\">{{cite web|last1=Shaw|first1=Chris|title=Tiago Ilori completes permanent move to Reading|url=http://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/first-team/249713-tiago-ilori-completes-permanent-move-to-reading|publisher=Liverpool FC|accessdate=18 January 2017}}</ref>\n| 2020<ref name=\"Ilori LFC\" />\n| 64\n| 1\n|-\n| 22\n| [[Pelle Clement]]\n| {{flagicon|NLD}}\n| MF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2019|5|5|1996|5|19}}\n| [[AFC Ajax]]\n| 2017<ref name=\"Royals sign Pelle Clement from Ajax\"/>\n| 2020<ref name=\"Royals sign Pelle Clement from Ajax\">{{cite web|title=Royals sign Pelle Clement from Ajax|url=https://www.readingfc.co.uk/news/2017/june/royals-sign-pelle-clement-from-ajax/|website=readingfc.co.uk|publisher=Reading F.C.|accessdate=28 June 2017|date=28 June 2017}}</ref>\n| 29\n| 0\n|-\n| 26\n| [[George Evans (footballer, born 1994)|George Evans]]\n| {{flagicon|ENG}}\n| CM\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2019|5|5|1994|12|13}}\n| [[Manchester City F.C.|Manchester City]]\n| 2016\n| 2019<ref name=\"Reading Sign Evans\">{{Cite news |title=Evans signs from Manchester City |url=http://www.readingfc.co.uk/news/article/george-evans-signs-from-manchester-city-2910744.aspx |publisher=Reading F.C. |accessdate=19 January 2016|date=19 January 2016}}</ref>\n| 72\n| 4\n|-\n| 37\n| [[Axel \u00d3skar Andr\u00e9sson|Axel Andr\u00e9sson]]\n| {{flagicon|ISL}}\n| DF\n| {{birth date and age2|df=yes|2019|5|5|1998|1|27}}\n| Academy\n| 2016<ref name=\"15 youngsters sign new pro deals with Reading\" />\n| 2020<ref name=\"Andresson 2020\"/>\n| 2\n| 